name: Loveless light
description:
Journal entry - wrap party photoshoot

"I feel myself - my heart… my heart pushes warm and forward as the breeze blowsssss us away. Sweet wonderful visceral reactions… visceral…as we connect. Connect. Living and breathing together. Together. Without a doubt incredible transfers… of of of something. For lack of understanding. Frequencies. Wonderful frequencies. Whatever capacity it may be, it seeps into everything. There is something, something… something so strangely vibrant, so so so intoxicating… as the highs of all drugs… in all the worlds… of beings… reach a similar high - high - high - climax - the peak of everything".

100% of the money raised will go to finishing this truly independent film and paying the artists. Four years of blood, sweat and tears. A cult classic in the making.

AUS/NZ Distribution: Pivot Pictures, Filmink Presents

PR + Trailer: https://www.grass-fires.com/blog/milesawaytrailer

4/10

Rolleiflex
